## 5.6 Combining bullet chart and sparklines

Step 1:


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
bullet <- coffeechain %>%
  filter(Date >= "2013-01-01") %>%
  group_by(`Product`) %>%
  summarise(`Target` = sum(`Budget Sales`),
            `Actual` = sum(`Sales`)) %>%
  ungroup() 
```
:::


Step 2:


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
sales_data = sales_data %>%
  left_join(bullet)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stderr}

```
Joining with `by = join_by(Product)`
```


:::
:::


Step 3:


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
sales_data %>%
  gt() %>%
  gt_plt_sparkline('Monthly Sales') %>%
  gt_plt_bullet(column = Actual, 
                target = Target, 
                width = 28,
                palette = c("lightblue", 
                          "black")) %>%
  gt_theme_538()
```

